    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2. Configuration"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "2.1. Port configuration"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "reference： 80-42841-1A_REV_AB_QAM8775P_Pin_Assignment_and_GPIO_Configuration_Spreadsheet.xlsm"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "configure SAIL_IO_0 and SAIL_IO_1 to SE0 by select PORT_PIN_MODE_1."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Both pins should configure as PORT_PIN_PULL_UP."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20I2C/image-2024-11-3_18-31-29.png?api=v2",
